## REQUEST BODY CREATION

This program exists to create an example request body you should run this program.

### RUNNING PROGRAM EXAMPLE

```
./<binary name> -cardUID "48 97 25 68"
```

### OUTPUT EXAMPLE

Json is valid request body

```
message input: 48972568
{"UUID":"0192ca40-5f76-7112-b369-a1e7a91985eb","content":""}
```
